channel.title: Happy Birthday!
channel.description:
It's only 4 days until we celebrate the day America officially declared that we were better [s]worse[/s] (Fat_Cookies u asshole :P) than Britain!
If you're an American, what do you plan to do on Independence day? If you're British, please don't cry over your lost colonies. If you're neither, move out of your third world country!
My Plans: My neighborhood pools our money together and puts on a rather large fireworks display.
